---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout title="Resources" description="Best resource farming methods ranked for Last War: Survival mid-game players.">
  <h1>Resources</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p><strong>Best farming methods (ranked for mid-game efficiency):</strong></p>
    <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 mt-1">
      <li><strong>Doom Elites with Monica</strong> — Highest return by far when she is in the squad.</li>
      <li><strong>Regular map elites</strong> — Consistent and low risk.</li>
      <li><strong>High-load gathering marches</strong> — Excellent when your troop load research is decent.</li>
      <li><strong>Event chests</strong> (especially during Arms Race and VS).</li>
      <li><strong>Alliance gifts + daily/weekly rewards</strong> — Passive but important.</li>
    </ol>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Resource Priority Order (Mid-Game)</h2>
  <p>Focus spending on what actually moves your main squad forward:</p>
  <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
    <li><strong>Hero Shards / Universal Shards</strong> — Stars are the biggest power spikes.</li>
    <li><strong>Gear materials &amp; Ore</strong> — Especially Mythic pieces for your top 3–4 heroes.</li>
    <li><strong>Skill Medals</strong> — Max active skills on your main DPS first.</li>
    <li><strong>Research speed &amp; troop-related tech</strong> — Directly increases your output.</li>
    <li><strong>Food / Energy</strong> — Only hoard what you need for training and healing.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Practical Tips</h2>
  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
    <li>Never let your stamina sit at max for long — use it on elites or events.</li>
    <li>Coordinate elite rallies in your alliance so multiple people bring Monica when possible.</li>
    <li>Keep at least one squad with high troop load dedicated to gathering during resource events.</li>
    <li>During Arms Race, save major chest pops for the final hours for better alliance gifts.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#8a96b0]">Hoarding resources without spending them on your main squad is one of the slowest ways to progress. Power compounds faster when you invest early and smartly.</p>
</Layout>